        "client_msg_id": "eff9a790-abf0-4e6f-a8cd-a49a7f3d943c",
        "type": "message",
        "text": "Hey Hillá! Yes, we give candidates like this a simple writing test--usually it’s something like “write a 400-500 word article about (topic relevant to our industry)“. We provide some simple guidance e.g. keywords, audience, goal, but we don’t provide a full-on brief. We send this with a note for context that our articles are usually 1,500 words but the idea is to write a complete, mini article in a condensed time frame.",
